Limited documentation available in the wiki.
 
http://wiki.github.com/psinnott/gntp-send


The Makefiles have been removed, it now relies on just cmake.

So in theory the steps should now be (on any platform):

    mkdir build && cd build
    ccmake ..  // fill in the detail for the build
    
    
    
    cmake --install . --config RELEASE
    or just build
    cmake --build . --config RELEASE
    or
    cmake --build . --target install --config DEBUG

